title: South Aussie with Cosi
overview: Cosi is a proud, born and bred South Australian who heads up South Aussie with Cosi. Since first airing in 2011, South Aussie with Cosi has fast become South Australia's favourite travel lifestyle show.Cosi is SA's biggest producer of TV in the state and very proud to employ only South Australians! South Aussie with Cosi is a household name, not only showcasing regional and city travel destinations but also promoting SA business, local lifestyle, well-being, community spirit, state history and everything in between!
